FBIS4-32637 "dreeu124_k_94007" FBIS-EEU-94-124 Daily Report 27 Jun 1994 CROATIA Tudjman Appoints Envoy for Contact Group Talks Tudjman Appoints Envoy for Contact Group Talks LD2706141894 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in Serbo-Croatian 1300 GMT 27 Jun 94 LD2706141894 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network Serbo-Croatian BFN [Text] On the basis of Article 99 of the Constitution of the Republic of Croatia, President of the Republic Franjo Tudjman has appointed Miomir Zuzul, the ambassador of the Republic of Croatia at the United Nations in Geneva, as special envoy of the president of the republic at the negotiations and work with the contact group and other representatives of the international community.
